## 📂 Datasets

This project uses the following datasets:

### 1. Bitcoin Market Sentiment (Fear & Greed Index)

This dataset contains the daily Bitcoin market sentiment classification (Fear or Greed), which is used to analyze its relationship with trader performance.

**Source:**  
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PgQC0tO8XN-wqkNyghWc_-mnrYv_nhSf/view?usp=sharing

---

### 2. Historical Trader Data (Hyperliquid)

This dataset contains historical trading activity from Hyperliquid, including trade execution details, position sizes, PnL, fees, and timestamps.

**Source:**  
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IAfLZwu6rJzyWKgBToqwSmmVYU6VbjVs/view?usp=sharing

